1
00:00:04,850 --> 00:00:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many dynamite punches will it 
take for you to fall, I wonder?!</font>

2
00:00:09,780 --> 00:00:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

3
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I already said... this is nothing to me.</font>

4
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's the best you've got...</font>

5
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you can keep it coming, 
and it won't matter!</font>

6
00:00:41,570 --> 00:00:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

7
00:00:50,060 --> 00:00:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

8
00:00:51,530 --> 00:00:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Sky Egg-exclusive All Might hoodie?!</font>

9
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:35,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an1}<font size="40"><font color="#c5000e">Catastrophe</font></font></b></font>

10
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:35,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}Great upheaval in society or the natural world.
 Major change.
 Can also refer to a tragic outcome in stories.
Often accompanied by destruction.</b></font>

11
00:02:34,220 --> 00:02:36,390
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><i>{\an1}<font size="30"><font color="#ffe640">Balloon Soul</font></font></i></b></font>

12
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're shaking again.</font>

13
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it really just an earthquake?</font>

14
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Control, this is Ingenium.</font>

15
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happening to the Sky Egg?</font>

16
00:02:55,350 --> 00:02:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pick up the phone, boss!</font>

17
00:02:56,950 --> 00:02:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Should I go check things out?</font>

18
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

19
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What now?</font>

20
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The power's out.</font>

21
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My phone!</font>

22
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't turn on anymore!</font>

23
00:03:20,490 --> 00:03:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine either.</font>

24
00:03:31,690 --> 00:03:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An EM pulse to shut down 
all the electronics...</font>

25
00:03:36,090 --> 00:03:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And make sure no one crashes 
the Captain's last stand.</font>

26
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's the layout of the Sky Egg.</font>

27
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the event of an earthquake 
or other disasters,</font>

28
00:03:50,770 --> 00:03:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the elevators shut down and the 
emergency stairwells open up.</font>

29
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the power rooms for each powered 
down while they were still locked.</font>

30
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, we're trapped.</font>

31
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it was done on purpose  
by a third party.</font>

32
00:04:08,260 --> 00:04:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if this isn't an accident 
or a natural disaster...</font>

33
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an attack, with malicious intent.</font>

34
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, you mean a terrorist attack?!</font>

35
00:04:16,730 --> 00:04:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Steady yourself, Death Arms.</font>

36
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heroes are meant to be a reassuring 
presence in emergencies—</font>

37
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can't let yourself unravel.</font>

38
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Tsukauchi, what's the 
status of Captain Celebrity?</font>

39
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unknown.</font>

40
00:04:30,890 --> 00:04:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

41
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we'll assume the worst case 
scenario, that he's incapacitated,</font>

42
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and respond with just the 
heroes on the scene here.</font>

43
00:04:39,710 --> 00:04:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to confirm the status 
inside and out of the building,</font>

44
00:04:41,710 --> 00:04:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">ensure the safety of the audience,</font>

45
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">establish a line to the outside, and 
prepare to intercept any enemies...</font>

46
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Based on our individual Quirks, we'll 
split up and handle these tasks.</font>

47
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fifty thousand lives are in our care, and 
we will not let a single one be lost.</font>

48
00:04:57,710 --> 00:05:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll combine our strengths 
to weave a safety net.</font>

49
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we agreed?</font>

50
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teamwork ain't my thing, but fine!</font>

51
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everybody, listen to me!</font>

52
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this shitty shaking and 
blackouts? An earthquake!</font>

53
00:05:15,690 --> 00:05:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or at least that's what we're 
led to believe, for now!</font>

54
00:05:18,890 --> 00:05:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You folks bear with us while we 
make sure everything's safe!</font>

55
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, sit still!</font>

56
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone is feeling sick, 
please let us know!</font>

57
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's an access port for the upper area 
of the dome that can be manually opened.</font>

58
00:05:45,690 --> 00:05:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't get us down 
to the ground, but...</font>

59
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll suffice.</font>

60
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:51,910
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#000608">Authorized Personnel Only
<font color="#4b161c">No Trespassing</font></font></b></font>

61
00:05:49,990 --> 00:05:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A group will head to the access port—</font>

62
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we can let a group with 
flight Quirks escape,</font>

63
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and establish contact with the outside.</font>

64
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can't re-establish power, 
let's arrange for transpo—</font>

65
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More shaking...</font>

66
00:06:07,220 --> 00:06:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Having CC around would be a real 
relief at a time like this.</font>

67
00:06:12,710 --> 00:06:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boss...</font>

68
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry! I almost dozed off there.</font>

69
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What with how those punches of yours have 
been so soothing, like a nice breeze.</font>

70
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, I'm wondering how much 
more you've got left in the tank.</font>

71
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blowing up your hands like 
that, over and over...</font>

72
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like you can 
regenerate forever, right?</font>

73
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we both stop 
wasting time like this?</font>

74
00:07:02,730 --> 00:07:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in the middle of work, y'know.</font>

75
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And dealing with you isn't 
part of this job...</font>

76
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just throwing in a bit of fan service!</font>

77
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You!</font>

78
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the man who's going 
to defend this tower</font>

79
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with the stuff that 
shoots out of my hands!</font>

80
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Crawler, Sky Egg version!</font>

81
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy, what are you doing?! 
Get out of here, now!</font>

82
00:07:39,780 --> 00:07:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't! He's been 
clobbering you, Captain!</font>

83
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:46,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I'm fine! Just look at me!</font>

84
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Act tough some other time! 
It's just annoying right now!</font>

85
00:07:50,710 --> 00:07:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, if I can nail his exploding fists 
with my projectiles, and detonate them...</font>

86
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'll save you from 
any more direct hits!</font>

87
00:08:01,170 --> 00:08:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rapid fire special...</font>

88
00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Crawler's SGBBBB!</font>

89
00:08:07,530 --> 00:08:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shooty-Go...</font>

90
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blam-Blam-Blam-Blam!</font>

91
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, boy. You've just made something 
really important clear to me.</font>

92
00:08:21,090 --> 00:08:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? What's that?!</font>

93
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just buying time 
here. Caught in a quagmire.</font>

94
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Without a lot of movement 
toward a resolution.</font>

95
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Considering that thing can regenerate...</font>

96
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind getting a little dirty!</font>

97
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if those blasts keep going 
off, I know what'll happen!</font>

98
00:08:40,690 --> 00:08:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heroes will show up!</font>

99
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're counting on someone else 
to save us, at a time like this?</font>

100
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:50,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doing my best while counting 
on others to do the same!</font>

101
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's always been my style!</font>

102
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not the smartest way 
of going about things,</font>

103
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but...</font>

104
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, we don't have 
a lot of other options!</font>

105
00:09:01,430 --> 00:09:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm counting on you, my boy!</font>

106
00:09:04,230 --> 00:09:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

107
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When that thing starts 
flying towards Captain...</font>

108
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I use my SGB to stop him!</font>

109
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to stay on the move
 and match his movements</font>

110
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'll always be in 
position to defend Cap</font>

111
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with another SGB!</font>

112
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I don't pay attention to 
maintaining the traction for my feet—</font>

113
00:09:39,290 --> 00:09:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll fall!</font>

114
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Be a little more careful, my boy!</font>

115
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:47,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thanks!</font>

116
00:09:48,770 --> 00:09:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you fall, I'll have 
no one defending me.</font>

117
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I go down, nothing will be 
holding the Sky Egg's dome up!</font>

118
00:09:57,780 --> 00:09:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All because of your carelessness!</font>

119
00:10:02,620 --> 00:10:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it! Maybe ease off 
with the pressure, please?!</font>

120
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got this, my boy!</font>

121
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was always popular.</i></font>

122
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I would fly around, people 
would happily wave at me.</i></font>

123
00:10:26,490 --> 00:10:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Adults, children, and especially girls.</i></font>

124
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then...</i></font>

125
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there, sweetheart! What's wrong?</font>

126
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I see someone with a sour look on their
face, I can't help but ask about it.</i></font>

127
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing. This is 
just how my face looks.</font>

128
00:11:11,430 --> 00:11:17,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, but I happen to know a magic 
spell for turning that frown upside down.</font>

129
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

130
00:11:22,690 --> 00:11:26,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been told this is more 
exciting than a rollercoaster!</font>

131
00:11:26,230 --> 00:11:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you get scared, just hold on 
tight and let out a scream—</font>

132
00:11:31,050 --> 00:11:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

133
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on, you're gonna fall!</font>

134
00:11:34,810 --> 00:11:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll put you down, just wait! One second!</font>

135
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I guess you didn't like it?</font>

136
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being forced onto a rollercoaster?! No!</font>

137
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention your smug 
smile being annoying!</font>

138
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one's ever said that about me before.</font>

139
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet! Why bother getting 
mad at a balloon?</font>

140
00:11:54,090 --> 00:11:55,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A balloon?</font>

141
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheery, flashy, and empty on the inside.</font>

142
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're talking about me?</font>

143
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's awful!</font>

144
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Hey! Good afternoon! I'm a balloon!"</font>

145
00:12:18,130 --> 00:12:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, I wanted to apologize 
about the other day.</font>

146
00:12:20,290 --> 00:12:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just wanted to make you happy.</font>

147
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still mad?</font>

148
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really.</font>

149
00:12:28,430 --> 00:12:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's good.</font>

150
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you might hate 
me or something...</font>

151
00:12:32,570 --> 00:12:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Considering how you glared 
at me when we first met.</font>

152
00:12:35,930 --> 00:12:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what that was.</font>

153
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just thought about how it must 
be fun to fly around like that.</font>

154
00:12:45,070 --> 00:12:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?! Then—</font>

155
00:12:47,050 --> 00:12:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more roller coaster 
rides for me, thanks.</font>

156
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only idiots and children 
enjoy that kind of thing.</font>

157
00:12:53,450 --> 00:12:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, how about a balloon ride then?</font>

158
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Balloon ride?</font>

159
00:13:02,110 --> 00:13:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are we so close to the ground?</font>

160
00:13:04,090 --> 00:13:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels ridiculous in 
a whole different way!</font>

161
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By your request, the balloon 
tour will now ascend!</font>

162
00:13:16,110 --> 00:13:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never wanted anyone to hate me.</i></font>

163
00:13:19,310 --> 00:13:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Especially when it came to girls.</i></font>

164
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I have to admit,</i></font>

165
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the idea of taming a such a surly 
young lady may have appealed to me.</i></font>

166
00:13:31,780 --> 00:13:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

167
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was the one who ended up being tamed.</i></font>

168
00:13:48,050 --> 00:13:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I went on a full-out 
offensive afterward.</i></font>

169
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:53,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Desperate for you to look my way.</i></font>

170
00:13:53,970 --> 00:13:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wanting to see your smile.</i></font>

171
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chris...</font>

172
00:14:01,050 --> 00:14:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might be a stupid idiot 
who always seems fishy,</font>

173
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but when I think about how most of 
the world is irredeemable trash...</font>

174
00:14:09,130 --> 00:14:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You start to seem pretty nice...</font>

175
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in comparison.</font>

176
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I take that as a "yes," then?</font>

177
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Chris! Knock it off! Do 
you want to make me mad?!</font>

178
00:14:28,340 --> 00:14:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honey, if it gets to be too much, 
just hold me tight and scream!</font>

179
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dummy.</font>

180
00:14:41,590 --> 00:14:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was so happy.</i></font>

181
00:14:44,810 --> 00:14:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The thought of being able to 
spend our lives together...</i></font>

182
00:14:47,410 --> 00:14:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And getting to see your smile every 
day for the rest of my life.</i></font>

183
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was what I thought at the time.</i></font>

184
00:15:00,930 --> 00:15:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Honey...</i></font>

185
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But ultimately, you were 
mad at me all the time.</i></font>

186
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I gradually started 
having trouble with work...</i></font>

187
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People I thought were my good friends</i></font>

188
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>used my name to swindle 
people out of money.</i></font>

189
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would think I was taking down a bad guy,</i></font>

190
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and then end up being sued, 
making me seem like the villain.</i></font>

191
00:15:26,890 --> 00:15:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder where it all went wrong?</i></font>

192
00:15:30,020 --> 00:15:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Honey, what should I 
have done differently?</i></font>

193
00:15:33,850 --> 00:15:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everything was so complicated, 
both at home and out in the world,</i></font>

194
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:41,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and even now, I'm not 
sure what the answer is.</i></font>

195
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Captain? What are you smiling about?</font>

196
00:15:49,380 --> 00:15:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me, just doing a bit of thinking.</font>

197
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're facing off with a powerful, 
exploding villain.</font>

198
00:15:57,090 --> 00:15:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have 50,000 lives 
resting on my shoulders.</font>

199
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A very easy to understand dilemma.</font>

200
00:16:02,730 --> 00:16:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even an idiot like me 
can't screw this one up!</font>

201
00:16:07,310 --> 00:16:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure I'd trade danger 
for complexity, myself.</font>

202
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait! He's putting his hands together—</font>

203
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crap! Captain!</font>

204
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A dud?</font>

205
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What have we got, Eraser?!</font>

206
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I managed to keep him from going 
off, but it's a temporary measure.</font>

207
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like the threat's actually gone.</font>

208
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if he flies to the other side of the
tower, my Erasure won't be able to reach.</font>

209
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't escape, villain!</font>

210
00:16:58,940 --> 00:16:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

211
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Best Jeanist! What's he standing on?!</font>

212
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the aerial escape team.</font>

213
00:17:06,330 --> 00:17:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've made contact 
and reported the scenario.</font>

214
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're now moving to deal 
with the villains!</font>

215
00:17:11,210 --> 00:17:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems the thread of 
hope has found its mark.</font>

216
00:17:31,350 --> 00:17:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna Fall!</font>

217
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:39,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Snipe! The flying villain 
that was above the dome is down!</font>

218
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ingenium.</font>

219
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got something for you from Airjet.</font>

220
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are the communicators 
we use on Team Idaten.</font>

221
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's establish an 
operational center here,</font>

222
00:17:51,410 --> 00:17:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where we can support 
and receive updates</font>

223
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">from the assorted heroes 
who are in action.</font>

224
00:17:56,450 --> 00:18:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, people, get those 
engines going at full throttle!</font>

225
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ninpo:</font>

226
00:18:11,370 --> 00:18:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thousand Sheet Pierce!</font>

227
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeanist!</font>

228
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeanist!</font>

229
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's here.</font>

230
00:18:23,290 --> 00:18:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time.</font>

231
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">High-capacity carbon fiber cables.</font>

232
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this gonna work? They're really heavy.</font>

233
00:18:35,610 --> 00:18:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be a problem.</font>

234
00:18:37,110 --> 00:18:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can weigh tens of tons...</font>

235
00:18:39,870 --> 00:18:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if they are in the form of fibers, 
they bow to my will as Fiber Master!</font>

236
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See, I was right! The heroes 
managed to save the day!</font>

237
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Well, if we're in the clear now...</font>

238
00:19:02,690 --> 00:19:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to ask you for something, Koichi.</font>

239
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up? Why so dramatic?</font>

240
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let my wife and baby know...</font>

241
00:19:15,530 --> 00:19:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That Daddy was a great hero.</font>

242
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure! I don't mind.</font>

243
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you two all right?</font>

244
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, we're fine! Hey, it's Edge Shot!</font>

245
00:19:28,550 --> 00:19:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you really ought to tell them 
that yourself when you get home.</font>

246
00:19:36,010 --> 00:19:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pushing my limits... taking 
it as far as I can...</i></font>

247
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never done anything 
like that before.</i></font>

248
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it's not a bad feeling.</i></font>

249
00:19:48,910 --> 00:19:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Say, honey...</i></font>

250
00:19:50,650 --> 00:19:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like I may have finally 
earned some praise from you.</i></font>

251
00:19:55,630 --> 00:19:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do you think? Was I cool?</i></font>

252
00:20:00,390 --> 00:20:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Would you be proud to 
call me your partner?</i></font>

253
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy?! What are you doing?!</font>

254
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain! Stop spacing out and fly!</font>

255
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And save me while you're at it!</font>

256
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have the strength anymore! 
That's why I'm falling!</font>

257
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What have you done?!</font>

258
00:20:21,710 --> 00:20:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kinda just got carried away!</font>

259
00:20:24,870 --> 00:20:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>God, heroes, anyone, please help!</i></font>

260
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't care about me, but save Koichi!</i></font>

261
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't let this brave boy die!</i></font>

262
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

263
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain and Crawler!</font>

264
00:20:43,970 --> 00:20:45,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this battle...</font>

265
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've contributed from the shadows!</font>

266
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which more than earns them our help!</font>

267
00:20:51,140 --> 00:20:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. Hell no.</font>

268
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't happening.</font>

269
00:20:55,440 --> 00:21:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You folks managed to hang on by the skin 
of your teeth, I'll give you that,</font>

270
00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you were outgunned from the get-go.</font>

271
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't obvious because 
I was trying to run an experiment.</font>

272
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turns out, I can kick off the 
climax whenever it suits me.</font>

273
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A detonation to get out 
of the restraints!</i></font>

274
00:21:19,470 --> 00:21:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not good! I can't see them 
inside of that smoke!</font>

275
00:21:23,430 --> 00:21:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention, frankly,</font>

276
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a bunch of nobodies pulling out all
the stops to make a big save...</font>

277
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">really pisses me off for some reason!</font>

278
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, you can all die!</font>

279
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Causing the exploding villain's 
body to limitlessly reproduce...</font>

280
00:21:48,930 --> 00:21:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for one big boom! Game over, man!</font>

281
00:23:25,390 --> 00:23:27,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things have never been more desperate!</font>

282
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, who else would show up 
other than the number one hero,</font>

283
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and my idol, All Might?!</font>

284
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: This Is a Hero!</font>

285
00:23:35,710 --> 00:23:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And in the shadows, my master 
begins a solo battle.</font>

